  },
  {
    "start": 353.5,
    "text": "Pros, I would say,"
  },
  {
    "start": 354.5,
    "text": "is not per se of like being a model only."
  },
  {
    "start": 357.5,
    "text": "I like the kind of like everyday's different."
  },
  {
    "start": 359.5,
    "text": "I can bring creativity into my job."
  },
  {
    "start": 361.5,
    "text": "Because everyday I'm a different person."
  },
  {
    "start": 363.5,
    "text": "Sometimes that allows you to explore like characters that maybe it's not who you are."
  },
  {
    "start": 367.5,
    "text": "Like if you are a mean person on camera,"
  },
  {
    "start": 369.5,
    "text": "you are allowed to be mean."
  },
  {
    "start": 370.5,
    "text": "So like you can experience how that person will feel."
  },
  {
    "start": 372.5,
    "text": "As someone who gets to meet a lot of people,"
