    "start": 378.5,
    "text": "what they do, what they like."
  },
  {
    "start": 379.5,
    "text": "Because I feel like you can learn a lot about hearing people's stories."
  },
  {
    "start": 384.5,
    "text": "So I love that about my job."
  },
  {
    "start": 386.5,
    "text": "I don't like that it's so uncertain."
  },
