    "start": 428.5,
    "text": "So it was only part time."
  },
  {
    "start": 429.5,
    "text": "So I didn't do as much work as I did here."
  },
  {
    "start": 431.5,
    "text": "In Spain, the work that I did was mostly fashion work or like a band work."
  },
  {
    "start": 437.5,
    "text": "It was in Korea, it's mostly commercial work more than modeling."
  },
  {
    "start": 441.5,
    "text": "So in Spain, I did more like cut off."
  },
  {
    "start": 444.5,
