  {
    "start": 870.5,
    "text": "that maybe it's not who you are."
  },
  {
    "start": 872.5,
    "text": "Like, if you are a mean person on camera,"
  },
  {
    "start": 874.5,
    "text": "you are allowed to be mean,"
  },
  {
    "start": 875.5,
    "text": "so you can experience how the person will feel."
  },
  {
    "start": 877.5,
    "text": "As someone who gets to meet a lot of people,"
  },
  {
    "start": 879.5,
    "text": "I generally like to meet people,"
  },
  {
    "start": 881.5,
    "text": "ask them questions about their life,"
  },
  {
    "start": 883.5,
    "text": "what they do, what they like."
  },
  {
    "start": 884.5,
    "text": "Because I feel like you can learn a lot"
  },
  {
    "start": 887.5,
    "text": "about hearing people's stories."
  },
  {
    "start": 889.5,
    "text": "So, I love that about my job."
  },
  {
    "start": 891.5,
    "text": "I don't like that it's so uncertain."
  },
  {
    "start": 893.5,
    "text": "Last minute, it's not going to be this day."
  },
  {
    "start": 895.5,
    "text": "It's going to be this other one."
  },
  {
    "start": 896.5,
    "text": "That's rough."
  },
  {
    "start": 897.5,
    "text": "So, it's a little bit hard to make a life around it"
  },
  {
    "start": 899.5,
    "text": "because you never really know what it's going to be like."
  },
  {
    "start": 902.5,
    "text": "I can understand that."
  },
  {
    "start": 903.5,
    "text": "It's very uncertain."
  },
  {
    "start": 904.5,
    "text": "So, it's like good on one side than the bad."
  },
  {
    "start": 906.5,
    "text": "It's very uncertain because you don't know who you're going to meet,"
  },
  {
    "start": 908.5,
    "text": "how it's going to go."
  },
  {
    "start": 909.5,
    "text": "Like, if it's going to be fun or not,"
  },
  {
    "start": 911.5,
    "text": "also there's a lot of waiting time."
  },
  {
    "start": 913.5,
    "text": "Sometimes it happens like shooting for 24 hours."
  },
  {
    "start": 915.5,
    "text": "And you're shooting one hour or two hours on the rest of the waiting."
  },
  {
    "start": 918.5,
    "text": "You get really tired by the end of it."
  },
  {
    "start": 920.5,
    "text": "Is there anything like you feel like being in a model in Korea"
  },
  {
    "start": 924.5,
    "text": "versus being a model in Spain?"
  },
  {
    "start": 926.5,
    "text": "Like, is there any difference, would you say?"
  },
  {
    "start": 929.5,
    "text": "I think when I did modeling in Spain, I was studying my master's degree."
  },
  {
    "start": 932.5,
    "text": "So, it was only part time."
  },
  {
    "start": 933.5,
    "text": "So, I didn't do as much work as I did here."
  },
  {
    "start": 936.5,
    "text": "In Spain, the work that I did was mostly fashion work or like a band work."
  },
  {
    "start": 941.5,
    "text": "It was in Korea, it's mostly commercial work, more than modeling."
  },
  {
    "start": 945.5,
    "text": "So, okay."
  },
  {
    "start": 946.5,
    "text": "So, in Spain, I did more like, cut off."
  },
  {
    "start": 948.5,
    "text": "Well, you did the language."
  },
  {
    "start": 949.5,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "start": 950.5,
    "text": "Or a band."
  },
  {
    "start": 951.5,
    "text": "I did that in Korea too, but like, that's amazing."
  },
  {
    "start": 953.5,
    "text": "That's amazing."
  },
  {
    "start": 954.5,
    "text": "Oh, I want to watch you."
  },
  {
    "start": 956.5,
    "text": "I make sure you see waving."
  },
  {
    "start": 957.5,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "start": 958.5,
    "text": "Good."
  },
  {
    "start": 959.5,
    "text": "Wow."
  },
  {
    "start": 960.5,
    "text": "We're nearing the end of our soup here."
  },
  {
    "start": 963.5,
    "text": "We did good."
  },
  {
    "start": 964.5,
    "text": "We killed it."
  },
  {
    "start": 965.5,
    "text": "It's almost all gone."
  },
  {
    "start": 967.5,
    "text": "What was the best?"
  },
  {
    "start": 968.5,
    "text": "I love this one."
  },
  {
    "start": 969.5,
    "text": "Shellfish."
  },
  {
    "start": 970.5,
    "text": "It's so good."
  },
  {
    "start": 971.5,
    "text": "Oh, I enjoyed it."
  },
  {
    "start": 972.5,
    "text": "Very much."
  },
  {
    "start": 973.5,
    "text": "Which one was your favorite?"
  },
  {
    "start": 974.5,
    "text": "I liked the noodles."
  },
  {
    "start": 975.5,
    "text": "Maybe the mussels."
  },
  {
    "start": 976.5,
    "text": "This is my first time."
  },
  {
    "start": 978.5,
    "text": "The mussels."
  },
  {
    "start": 979.5,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "start": 980.5,
    "text": "I liked it."
  },
  {
    "start": 981.5,
    "text": "Any of the shellfish."
  },
  {
    "start": 982.5,
    "text": "Nice."
  },
  {
    "start": 983.5,
    "text": "I just love that."
  },
  {
    "start": 984.5,
    "text": "I'm your first guest."
  },
  {
    "start": 985.5,
    "text": "I'm going."
  },
  {
    "start": 986.5,
    "text": "Thank you so much, everybody, for watching our very first episode of Lunch Hour English."
  },
  {
    "start": 990.5,
    "text": "Please stay tuned because we're going to have more guests and eat more delicious food."
  },
  {
    "start": 996.5,
    "text": "If you liked this video, make sure to subscribe to our channel."
  },
  {
    "start": 999.5,
    "text": "Like the video and comment below guys."
  },
  {
    "start": 1002.5,
    "text": "Thank you so much."
  },
  {
    "start": 1003.5,
    "text": "And thank you, Lorena."
  },
  {
    "start": 1004.5,
    "text": "Thank you very much."
  },
  {
    "start": 1005.5,
    "text": "Thank you very much."
  },
  {
    "start": 1006.5,
    "text": "Such a lovely guest."
  },
  {
    "start": 1007.5,
    "text": "I love having this conversation with you."
  },
  {
    "start": 1009.5,
    "text": "Come back and eat with me anytime."
  },
  {
    "start": 1011.5,
    "text": "Alright."
  },
  {
    "start": 1012.5,
    "text": "Bye, everyone."
  }
]